in the world 
it took just five notes for those 10 people to say whos 
this playing it must be menuhin or kreisler thomas j 
beckiewicz executive director of the annual contest said 
wednesday when you have 10 of the most expert violinists in the 
world you cannot fake anything 
singer 26 was sent home to sao paolo brazil on tuesday she 
had performed in sundays preliminary competition 
she was the first person accused of fraud in the contests 
eightyear history 
