the united states is deploying 
missile batteries multiple rocket launchers and mines in saudi 
arabias northern desert to blunt any possible iraqi thrust 
military officials say 
in the last two days patriot missile batteries designed to 
shoot down incoming missiles and multiple rocket launchers used to 
smash troop buildups have been brought in to reinforce us 
positions closest to the kuwaiti border 
