huge convoys that also carried hundreds of troops to forward camps 
us marines at a base camp close to the kuwaiti border said 
they were preparing to mine strategic northsouth roads but were 
taking special precautions to protect refugees fleeing kuwait 
mines will be placed along a side road running south from 
