it is a real booger to try to find and isolate shuttle boss 
robert crippen said after the mission was scrubbed wednesday 7 
hours before columbia was to have lifted off at 120 am today 
with the 150 million astro observatory 
engineers worked on a troubleshooting plan through the night 
