i think this leak has been there all along he said 
trying to isolate it out from the other leak confused the 
data 
my first reaction was frustration said program scientist ed 
weiler but my next thought was my god im glad they stopped 
some of my friends are aboard hydrogen is highly combustiblle 
the seven columbia crewmen left for their training base in 
