major british production this year his 1984 sunday in the park 
with george finished a 15week run june 16 at the royal national 
theater 
into the woods won three tony awards including one for 
sondheims score but some critics saw it as a schizophrenic work 
whose halves never quite meshed 
the first act sends such fairy tale characters as little red 
riding hood and cinderella into the woods where all end up 
