contributions from outside the state harkin responds that he has 
backed campaign finance legislation thwarted by republicans in 
congress 
both candidates are veteran campaigners harkin represented 
southwest iowas 5th district for 10 years before ousting incumbent 
republican sen roger jepsen in 1984 tauke has represented the 
heavily democratic 2nd district for 12 years 
