was not the uncertain ending but cutting the wealth of material to 
fit a twohour format 
i think this is a story that could have happened in any 
american city he said it offers some broad national lessons 
you cant say enough about the horror of violence against women and 
children that one reason alone would be enough for me to make this 
movie 
